name: SUCCESS FUEL - Team 29
description:
PITCH

In Success Fuel, you control a plane that circles a planet. The goal :  dodge the buildings and collect as many barrels of fuel as possible to stay in flight. Watch out for the various obstacles scattered around the planet !

CONTROLS CREDITS

GD : Tom BECKER - Tom GRANDJEAN MAGLIONE

GA : Jeanne CABON - Manasseh RAKOTOASIMBOLA

GP : Adrien RIBEIRO - Siméon MALARET - Thomas RAULIN

PRODUCER : Olivier DE BENOIST - Charlotte LITTO
